  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was like this, which was also a strange to us, but we find this only out later on, usually, in a tram car, it's about two or three sections where passengers go on and off.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you can also put a wagon and couple it to a tram car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And provided it's on the rails and the dimensions are in comparison to that of the rail, it will go through just like a ordinary train.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So once we finished constructing that rail so there was the link from the railway section outside the ghetto to transfer the goods onto the tram car section, and it went right through a very, very long road into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was very useful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
